;:7976401,&quot;user_id&quot;:5240021}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/mishtermoshter"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-cyan.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/mishtermoshter">MishterMoshter</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-06-18 09:16:22"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7976401">12 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Never in my entire life has a game made me say &quot;HELL YEAH&quot; so much. this whole game was so amazing, the music, the art, the dialogue, everything so natural and perfect. i&#x27;d clear my memory just to feel that joy i felt playing the game for the first time again. fucken spectacular.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div id="post-7974544" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7974544,&quot;user_id&quot;:1022069}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/superfreq"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-blue.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/superfreq">superfreq</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-06-17 21:59:19"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7974544">12 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+2)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Hi there!<br>I am creating a collection of fully blind accessible games, and your&nbsp;game is listed under the &quot;blind support tag&quot;.&nbsp; The word &quot;blind&quot; means different things to different people,&nbsp;and within that wide spectrum their are various levels of expertise with visual UI&#x27;s.&nbsp;&nbsp;but as a fully blind gamer, I am wondering what features this game provides for those who can not see the screen at all.&nbsp; Do you have &quot;screen reader&quot; or &quot;text to speech&quot; support?&nbsp; Is your game fully playable with a keyboard or controller, rather than having to point the mouse at buttons on the interface? If the answer to those questions is no, it would still be great to know what options are provided for those with less severe visual impairments, so that I might make them aware of your game&#x27;s usability for them.&nbsp;&nbsp;Thank you for any information you can provide, it&#x27;s very much appreciated!&nbsp;:)</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-7997818" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7997818,&quot;user_id&quot;:39368}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/paranoidhawk"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1hZ2UyL3VzZXIvMzkzNjgvODYxODkzLnBuZw==/25x25%23/CfFki6.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/paranoidhawk">paranoidhawk</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-06-22 01:36:19"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7997818">8 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Hi, thanks for reaching out, what you&#x27;re doing seems really cool. Lookouts does indeed have screen reader / text to speech support for the game and its menus. I believe the whole game should be playable solely through keyboard, but whether that is actually possible or a good experience I&#x27;m not as sure of. There are some other accessibility options as well such as changing textbox and text colour for different contrasts. If you&#x27;d like to chat more or discuss the game&#x27;s accessibility features please feel free to email us at marbleclaws (at) gmail dot com.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-7973342" class="community_post has_vote_column" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7973342,&quot;user_id&quot;:8261359}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fparanoidhawk.itch.io%2Flookouts&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/thatonemotorbike-0107"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-blue.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_au